          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " from Rep. Raja Krishnamoorthi, D-Ill., USPS Board of Governors Chairman Robert Duncan confirmed that, while leading the postal service, he ",
