            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " found that those removals had been planned for months, but that internal documents referred to them as a “reduction” in equipment.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The USPS also implemented new delivery policies under the guise of cutting costs. The Postal Service ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
